code: import $api from"../http/index";export default class noteService{static async add(note){const res=await $api.post('/note',note);return res.data;}static async edit(note){const res=await $api.put('/note',note);return res.data;}static async delete(note){const res=await $api.delete('/note',{params:{id:note._id}});return res.data;}static async get(){const res=await $api.get('/note');return res.data;}}
